description: A blurry close-up shows a man with aviator sunglasses and a red shirt.
A thin, dark, squiggly line appears in the bottom right corner of a light teal frame.
A blurry image shows a crowd of people, one of whom is wearing a pink shirt with a small, dark, heart-shaped patch.
A low-angle, slightly distorted view of a tall building's facade with numerous windows is presented.
A grainy image shows a shirtless man and a man wearing glasses and a dark t-shirt with a design.
A blurry, slightly overexposed close-up shot shows a group of men, one of whom wears glasses and a patterned tie.
A person holds a sign that reads "OUR GREAT WEAP" and another reads "DEVOTEES OF CIVIL RIGHTS."
A blurry, pixelated image shows a person wearing a dark green shirt or jacket with the word "Military" visible on the front.
A blurry, grainy crowd of people walks down a street in front of a large building with columns.
The image is a blank white page with a few small, faint specks.
A blurry, grainy shot shows a parade moving down a city street, with spectators lining the sidewalks and teal balloons floating above.
A blurry, slightly out-of-focus shot shows people, possibly on bicycles, and one person in the foreground appears to be wearing a large necklace or decorative garment.
A partially visible sign reads "OF CIVIL RIGHTS" and parts of other signs and a person are also visible.
A grainy, low-light photo shows a group of people standing near a banner with text.
A blurry image shows a sign that reads "CAPITALISM IS THE REAL OPPRESSION".
A blurry, grainy image shows a crowd of people near a police car.
A blurry image shows two people, one wearing a red shirt and sunglasses, and the other wearing a patterned shirt.
A crowd of people holds signs and banners at a protest or demonstration.
A grainy, discolored image shows a person wearing a light-colored tank top and hat.
A crowd of people stands on a city sidewalk, some facing the camera and others facing away.
